message:
Although the words ''first'' and ''lady'' aren't proper nouns themselves, the words in the context that it is;
1: A specific name for an occupation
2: A specific placeholder given to the holder of the occupation in question
gives the obligation that it is a proper noun.
This is just a small fix.
